---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Research | Aadit Agrawal">
	<section id="research" class="section">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2 class="label-text">RESEARCH & WRITING</h2>
			<div class="line"></div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="exp-list">
			<article class="exp-card">
				<div class="exp-header">
					<h3>FL + Digital Twin for Route Optimisation <span class="exp-at">@ SCE, MAHE</span></h3>
					<span class="label-text font-mono">JUN 2024—JUL 2025</span>
				</div>
				<p>GPS telemetry at 500K+ datapoints; dashcam CV with OpenCV + YOLO on 12,000+ labelled samples. Built a federated learning pipeline for privacy-preserving route optimisation across distributed edge nodes.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="exp-card">
				<div class="exp-header">
					<h3><a href="https://blog.ecitis.org">ECITIS Technical Blog - 18 Published Guides</a> <span class="exp-at">@ Dr. TMA Pai Endowment Chair, MAHE</span></h3>
					<span class="label-text font-mono">SEP 2025-PRES</span>
				</div>
				<p>Authored long-form technical references on: TensorRT-LLM/Triton production serving, AMD ROCm, Apple MLX, RLHF/DPO, MoE architectures, edge AI, LLM fine-tuning (LoRA/QLoRA), HPC optimization, and VLMs.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
